      "seed": 2042731104,
      "version": 888,
      "versionNonce": 726159968,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1770826715302,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Time-series data model\n    i. Raw sensor data\n    ii. Aggregated data (avg, min, max)\n\n2. Device registry\n    i. Device ID\n    ii. Firmware version\n    iii. Battery type\n\n3. Alert engine\n    Rule-based (before AI)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
